Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.93,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.48,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:40.06,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.65,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.65,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.57,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.99,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:55.45,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:03:00.33,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.80,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.26,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.60,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:21.84,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace in the great war against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.18,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was overwhelmed by unbearable sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.65,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we go back in time ten years, to East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:35.10,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is the story of the brothers\NLuffy and Ace, when they were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.90,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace isn't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.75,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.95,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:58.80,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,But the military is at the Gray Terminal, going there in your condition is far too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.01,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how big that fire was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.30,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,The chances they survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:09.67,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the chance is slim, we want to believe that the Boss and Ace survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.03,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra is looking for them right now.\NLet's just leave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.73,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,This is difficult for us all, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.61,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They shot the fishing boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.91,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Is the child alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.58,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He must have angered the Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.16,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.21,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  The ship's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.65,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd they suddenly fire at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.51,Main,Bodyguard,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Jalmac!  There's a child on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:42.93,Main,Saint Jalmac,0000,0000,0000,,He's flying a pirate flag so he's a pirate.  It doesn't matter who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.48,Main,Saint Jalmac,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:50.94,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.06,Main,Saint Jalmac,0000,0000,0000,,A mere commoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.44,Main,Saint Jalmac,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had the nerve to sail beside my ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.29,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  What was with that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:24.67,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,How could he anger the Celestial Dragon on the day of this important ceremony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.20,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Move the wreckage out of their way, quickly!  { def: tlc, from manga }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.08,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.58,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!  They've...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.75,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.12,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,They've returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.70,Main,Bandits,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:24.28,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:28.24,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Those injuries looks horrible... Hurry!  Tend to the Boss's wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.39,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.03,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.70,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.33,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.24,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.38,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What're you crying for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.92,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like I'm dead when I'm not, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.34,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let him be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.01,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.25,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, about the night of the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.57,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,After we took Luffy and left,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.07,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,what happened to you and the Boss\Nwhen you stayed behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.65,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,After you left, we fought Bluejam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.72,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to defeat him somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.44,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,And then we tried to catch up with you guys as fast as we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.94,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But by that time, the path had already been blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.24,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  There's no way out!  { def: this could be flashback style }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.82,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter, we have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.16,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.12,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:08:03.26,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,I told everyone that I was taking\Nfull responsibility for bringing you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.21,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Stay behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.21,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get separated from me, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.67,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.90,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dadan!  Are you alright?!  Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:31.57,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it out of the fire,\Nbut Dadan suffered horrible burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:36.00,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We found a hiding spot where the fire wouldn't reach us, by the river in the Middle Forest. {Okay, so it seems I completely neglected to mention that this forest had a name before, even though its name was shown in the captions back in 494. Damn, I fail.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:45.08,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!  Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.69,Main,Police,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.79,Main,Police,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:53.72,Main,Police,0000,0000,0000,,I went into the city in order to\Nsteal medicine, and get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.59,Main,Police,0000,0000,0000,,Then I tried desperately to keep Dadan alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:08.11,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me... Just go, Ace. { def: that's some hardcore hair she's got.  even fire can't touch it. }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:12.40,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool!  You took full responsibility for bringing me back, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.37,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.98,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  If anyone survived,\Nthey could be hiding around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.16,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Start looking!  Don't miss anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.06,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.70,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, so that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:33.08,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad you both made it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.85,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:39.65,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought something like this\Ncould happen to the Gray Terminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.60,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sabo is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:49.33,Main,Saint Jalmac,0000,0000,0000,,More insolent commoners might show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.87,Main,Saint Jalmac,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to be on the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:52.54,Main,Bodyguards,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Sabo's up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:05.33,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm glad Ace came back,\Nand Dadan is getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.04,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.00,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I... {Copy-paste from 502}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.25,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,will not run away! {End copy-paste from 502}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.46,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.31,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, my blood just\Nstarts rushing to my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:24.35,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like, if I run, I'll lose something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:24.93,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.73,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.82,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know for sure, but I think that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.74,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Even when he was up against a huge army and had no chance of winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.70,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Roger stood his ground, he never ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.80,Flashbacks,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Did he want to die or something?\NFleeing is a way to fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.71,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,True, but he never ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:53.60,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Because the people he held dear were behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:57.26,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,If they ran away together,\Nhis crewmates' lives would be in danger too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.45,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, it's not that he never ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:05.97,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,but rather, he didn't want the enemy to go after his crew.  So he never let the enemy get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.48,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,When he was like that, Roger truly was a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:13.98,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,There were times when he annihilated entire armies, just because they spoke badly of his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:18.81,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,True, if you made him mad, he was brutal, short-tempered and selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:24.46,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,However, those actions were always as simple and honest as those of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.34,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he grew up similar to how Ace is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:31.92,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,He truly hated the thought of losing his loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:41.13,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,It was his reckless lifestyle, and the luck\Nthat kept him alive, that made him the Pirate King. { def: tlc from manga }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:47.50,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,He had an awful reputation around the world, but the trust he earned from his crew was immeasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:52.32,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm a marine, I could never bring myself to hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.10,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I decided to take care of Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.15,Flashbacks,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones taking care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.94,Flashbacks,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  It sounds like you've got a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.49,Flashbacks,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.54,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Roger is still despised by society to this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:12.79,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that even if Ace despises his father,\Nhe still carries his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.63,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright... Who's gonna win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.88,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You went looking for Ace and Dadan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.05,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,They've both come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.89,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Really, they have?  That's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.06,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.48,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.23,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.57,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even joke about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.73,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.52,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a lie, nor a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:45.53,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,It was so sudden, I barely realized what had happened.  I doubted my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.66,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if it was just a dream or an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.08,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  Sabo went back to his noble born parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.58,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd sail out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.64,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!  Sabo went home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.86,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Outlaws like us understand how he must have felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.36,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,We all have places we really don't want to go back to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:08.97,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think he'd go to sea... if he was actually happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:14.62,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think he'd fly a pirate flag\Nand set out on his own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.45,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.07,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He really wasn't happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.16,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Even with parents, I'm still alone! {Copy-paste from 496.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:38.96,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why didn't we try to break him out of there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:44.39,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the person who killed Sabo?!  I'm gonna murder him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.18,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Celestial Dragon?!  There's no way you can do th{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.84,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna avenge his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.34,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.18,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it, you damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.14,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.35,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:00.67,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You keep acting tough, even though you don't have any real strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:04.48,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you can do now?!  You'll just end up dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:09.64,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die, and everyone will forget you by tomorrow!  That's all you amount to right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:15.20,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,It was this kingdom that killed Sabo!\NIt was the world itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.63,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.67,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's death brought about a new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:26.84,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Once you become a man of his caliber,\Nthen you're free to live or die as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.70,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Go tie up this moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.85,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:38.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:39.48,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:46.60,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  Men aren't supposed to be sobbing like that, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:04.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:11.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.73,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down a little, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.09,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Untie him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:25.73,Main,Bandits,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.82,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll loosen these right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.32,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.89,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,He cried all night.  He's asleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:37.24,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!  You have to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.08,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a letter!  From Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.96,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,He sent a letter before setting out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.21,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.59,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I won't go into the city.\NThat letter is addressed to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:16:00.40,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Luffy.  I hope you weren't hurt in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:03.24,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried, but I believe that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:09.51,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this, but by the time you read this letter, I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.40,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,out at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.36,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,A lot has happened, and I've decided to set sail ahead of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:26.86,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,My destination won't be in this country, but elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.29,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,There, I will become stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.97,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:39.61,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become pirates with more freedom than anyone else, and meet up again someday.  The three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:46.21,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere out on the wide, free ocean... I'm sure that someday, we'll meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.96,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.95,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who's the older brother between the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.21,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Two eldest sons, and one younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:03.04,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,It might be strange, but\Nthis bond between us is my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.92,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy might still be a weakling and a crybaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.75,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,but he's our brother!  Take care of him for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.80,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean, "Inspections"?!  They've just been holding one big welcome party all week!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:59.33,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't written anything regarding the Sabo-incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.60,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't seem like his parents have pressed charges either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:06.82,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they might be nobles, but they're up against the World Government and the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.69,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Suing them wouldn't accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.36,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Is Luffy still acting the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.10,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He barely even eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.18,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least that leaves more food for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:19.45,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,The Sabo incident must have really hit him hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.68,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!  Luffy! {Copy-paste from 496}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.62,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us have to set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.77,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out of this country and be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.32,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,With this, starting today, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.65,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.55,Flashbacks,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! {End copy-paste from 496}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.80,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep moping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:31.14,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,All the treasure we hid in the Middle Forest is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:37.88,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was stolen by survivors from Bluejam's crew, or maybe the military found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.82,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.13,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But that pile of loot doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:49.45,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo and I were gonna use it.  It was our Pirate Fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:53.02,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the end, Sabo didn't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:56.80,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'm not gonna bother with it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:00.57,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in gathering treasure if we can't even look after it.
