Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.78,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,And even stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:31.11,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll be able to protect anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.33,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have to lose anyone ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:41.80,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.83,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:46.61,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more worried\Nabout yourself than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:48.72,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You're way weaker than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.64,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, and remember this, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.35,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I will not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.06,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo made that request too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:06.11,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.  I will not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:10.40,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd die and leave behind a weakling of a brother like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:19.75,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not all that smart, so I don't know what killed Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:23.90,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever it was, it was something opposed to freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.97,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo died without ever gaining his freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.55,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But the two of us, who shared\Na toast with Sabo, are still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.10,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,So, listen up, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:43.12,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We will definitely live life without regrets! {Copy-paste from 459.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:03.88,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Noblemen only become true nobles once they turn eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:08.64,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I will leave this kingdom when I turn seventeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.20,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, we will set out to sea, {Copy-paste from 459}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:19.10,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,and live life the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.84,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,With more freedom than anyone else!{End copy-paste from 459}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:28.21,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that will make lots of people into our enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.50,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps will become our enemy, too.\NWe'll be risking our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:35.67,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cast off when we turn seventeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.60,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,We will become pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:12.14,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace have been struck by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:15.04,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But, inside their hearts, they both keep their determination to become pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:16.74,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and start looking towards the future once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:19.16,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, the time comes for their departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They set off, to live the dream Sabo could not fulfill!
